Package: GCSFilesystem
Type: Package
Title: Mounting a Google Cloud bucket as local drive
Version: 1.0
Date: 2020-08-27
Author: Jiefei Wang
Maintainer: Jiefei Wang <szwjf08@gmail.com>
Description: The package can mount a Google Cloud bucket as a local drive on your machine. You can browse and read files as if they are local files. For using the package, you need to install GCSDokan on Windows and gcsfuse on Linux and MacOs.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends:
  R (>= 4.0.0)
